<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12181&amp;p=138257#p138257"><![CDATA[
Maybe the game doesn't reset the RNG correctly.  The only time Pac-man uses a RNG is when the blue ghosts come to an intersection.<br />The original arcade game always resets the RNG at the start of every level, but it seems that the NES version does not.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Mon Dec 29, 2014 2:56 pm</p><hr />
